  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Global Database Project on Slavery (the pilot phase)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall objective of this project is to build a prototype database containing a comprehensive set of country-based information, including reliable estimates on slavery, risk factors related to socio-economic conditions and an overview of national responses against this crime. The ILO and Walk Free will collaborate to design the architecture of the prototype and to test its usefulness by producing a limited set of country profiles.</narrative>
  </description>
